# Terraform AWS EC2 Deployment

This project deploys an EC2 instance on AWS using Terraform.

## Features

- AWS Provider
- Variables
- Outputs
- EC2 Instance
- Resource Tagging

## Prerequisites

- AWS Account
- AWS CLI Configured
- Terraform Installed

## Usage

terraform init

terraform plan

terraform apply

terraform destroy

## Outputs

- Instance ID
- Public IP
- Public DNS